<text><body>
<cb:mulu level="1" n="13" type="其他">12 請佛三昧印</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<milestone n="2" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0094a23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0094a24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0094a25" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="002" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="002" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>千眼千臂觀世音菩薩陀羅尼神
<lb n="0094a26" ed="T"/>呪經卷下</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0094a27" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0094a28" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0094016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（大）＋唐【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唐【大】，大唐【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094016"><lem wit="【大】">唐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">大唐</rdg></app>總持寺<anchor xml:id="fxT20p0094a02"/>三藏沙門智通譯</byline>
<lb n="0094a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0094a2901">爾時觀世音菩薩。說是呪時三千大千世界。
<pb n="0094b" xml:id="T20.1057b.0094b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0094b01" ed="T"/>乃至非想非非想天六反震動。色究竟天摩
<lb n="0094b02" ed="T"/>醯首羅戰慄不<note n="0094017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">安＋（其處）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">安【大】，安其處【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094017"><lem wit="【大】">安</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">安其處</rdg></app>皆大<note n="0094018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">恐懼＝懼恐【宋】</note><note n="0094018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恐懼【大】，懼恐【宋】</note><app n="0094018"><lem wit="【大】">恐懼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">懼恐</rdg></app>。一切惡鬼皆
<lb n="0094b03" ed="T"/>大叫喚受大苦惱。東西散走莫知所趣。爾時
<lb n="0094b04" ed="T"/>化身語諸大眾及諸惡鬼神等。若不隨順我
<lb n="0094b05" ed="T"/>呪者。違逆者頭破粉碎。此呪能摧<note n="0094019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">碎＝破【宋】</note><note n="0094019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">碎【大】，破【宋】</note><app n="0094019"><lem wit="【大】">碎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">破</rdg></app>諸山乾
<lb n="0094b06" ed="T"/>竭大海。此呪能摧伏阿脩羅軍護諸國土。此
<lb n="0094b07" ed="T"/>呪能摧伏一切諸惡鬼<note n="0094020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">神＋（一切諸宿）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神【大】，神一切諸宿【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094020"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">神一切諸宿</rdg></app>。一切諸病一切惡
<lb n="0094b08" ed="T"/>毒。一切惡人。此呪能摧破三十三天皆令降
<lb n="0094b09" ed="T"/>伏。<note n="0094021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若＋（有）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，若有【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094021"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">若有</rdg></app>善男子有能誦持此呪者。其人威力說
<lb n="0094b10" ed="T"/>不可盡。此呪能令誦持之者豪貴自在。亦能
<lb n="0094b11" ed="T"/>令國王終身愛念。稱意所求悉皆滿足。若欲
<lb n="0094b12" ed="T"/>降伏魔怨者。<note n="0094022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當＋（分）【宋】</note><note n="0094022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，當分【宋】</note><app n="0094022"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">當分</rdg></app>燒<note n="0094023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">求＋（求）【元】</note><note n="0094023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">求【大】，求求【元】</note><app n="0094023"><lem wit="【大】">求</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">求求</rdg></app>羅<note n="0094024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">香＝若【宋】，（若）＋香【元】</note><note n="0094024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">香【大】，若【宋】，若香【元】</note><app n="0094024"><lem wit="【大】">香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">若</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">若香</rdg></app>誦我身呪二十
<lb n="0094b13" ed="T"/>一遍。若欲令一切人愛己者。呪楊枝二十一
<lb n="0094b14" ed="T"/>遍。口中嚼之即得愛敬。若欲令自身辯才智
<lb n="0094b15" ed="T"/>慧者。呪菖<note n="0094025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蒲＝莆【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蒲【大】，莆【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094025"><lem wit="【大】">蒲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">莆</rdg></app>一千八遍。塗其心上即得辯才
<lb n="0094b16" ed="T"/>無礙。作姥陀羅尼<note n="0094026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心＋（呪）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，心呪【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094026"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">心呪</rdg></app>印。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0094b17" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="14" type="其他">13 辯才無礙印咒</cb:mulu><head><note n="0094027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（菩薩）＋辯【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辯【大】，菩薩辯【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094027"><lem wit="【大】">辯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">菩薩辯</rdg></app>才無礙印<note n="0094028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔呪〕－【宋】</note><note n="0094028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呪【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0094028"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>第十三</head>
<lb n="0094b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0094b1801">以兩手相背合掌。大母指向前舒。此印能自
<lb n="0094b19" ed="T"/>護護他。當須結界隨所遊方。或呪淨水或呪
<lb n="0094b20" ed="T"/>淨灰各呪七遍。所在住處以手<note n="0094029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">掬＋（一<g ref="#CB13732"/>）【宋】</note><note n="0094029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">掬【大】，掬一<g ref="#CB13732"/>【宋】</note><app n="0094029"><lem wit="【大】">掬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">掬一<g ref="#CB13732"/></rdg></app>水掬灰先
<lb n="0094b21" ed="T"/>灑自身。然後向於<note n="0094030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔四方〕－【宋】</note><note n="0094030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四方【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0094030"><lem wit="【大】">四方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>四角如法散灑。若有
<lb n="0094b22" ed="T"/>善男子善女人。被諸惡鬼眾邪魍魎之所惑
<lb n="0094b23" ed="T"/>亂者。取石榴枝及柳枝。陰誦此呪輕打病人
<lb n="0094b24" ed="T"/>無病不差。呪<note n="0094031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔曰〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094031"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0094b25" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT20p0094b2501">南無薩婆<note n="0094032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛＝勃【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，勃【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094032"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">勃</rdg></app>陀達摩僧祇比耶　南無阿利
<lb n="0094b26" ed="T"/>耶婆盧吉低攝伐羅<note n="0094033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02746"/>＝寫【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094033" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02746"/>【大】，寫【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094033"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB02746"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">寫</rdg></app>　菩提薩多<note n="0094034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跛＝波【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跛【大】，波【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094034"><lem wit="【大】">跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">波</rdg></app>寫
<lb n="0094b27" ed="T"/>南無<note n="0094035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跋＝拔【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">跋【大】，拔【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094035"><lem wit="【大】">跋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">拔</rdg></app>折<note n="0094036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝囉【宋】</note><note n="0094036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅【大】，囉【宋】</note><app n="0094036"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">囉</rdg></app>波尼寫菩提薩多波寫　跢姪
<lb n="0094b28" ed="T"/>他　徒比徒比迦耶　徒比婆羅闍婆羅尼馺
<lb n="0094b29" ed="T"/>皤訶</p>
<pb n="0094c" xml:id="T20.1057b.0094c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0094c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0094c0101">此呪印能降伏諸邪見外道。若有善男子善
<lb n="0094c02" ed="T"/>女人。於晨朝時日三時。各誦一遍者。即與
<lb n="0094c03" ed="T"/>種種供養十億諸佛無有異也。永不受女身。
<lb n="0094c04" ed="T"/>命終之後永離三塗。即得往生阿彌陀佛國。
<lb n="0094c05" ed="T"/>如來授手摩頂。汝莫怖懼來生我國。現身不
<lb n="0094c06" ed="T"/>被橫死。不為鬼神之所得便。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0094c07" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="15" type="其他">14 破三千大三世界滅罪印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0094037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（菩薩）＋破【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">破【大】，菩薩破【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094037"><lem wit="【大】">破</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">菩薩破</rdg></app><note n="0094038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三千大三＝大千【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三千大三【大】，大千【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094038"><lem wit="【大】">三千大三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">大千</rdg></app>世界<note n="0094039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔滅〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滅【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094039"><lem wit="【大】">滅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>罪印第十四</head>
<lb n="0094c08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0094c0801">起立以左手向前展臂。五指向前散<note n="0094040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">托＝託【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">托【大】，託【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094040"><lem wit="【大】">托</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">託</rdg></app>竪五
<lb n="0094c09" ed="T"/>指。次以右手大母指屈在掌中。以四指<note n="0094041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">把拳＝捧【宋】</note><note n="0094041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">把拳【大】，捧【宋】</note><app n="0094041"><lem wit="【大】">把
<lb n="0094c10" ed="T"/>拳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">捧</rdg></app>當右耳上當。誦身呪頭指來去。此印日別
<lb n="0094c11" ed="T"/>須三時一時誦七遍。能滅五逆四重罪。於一
<lb n="0094c12" ed="T"/>切眾生生慈<note n="0094042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慈＝悲【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慈【大】，悲【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094042"><lem wit="【大】">慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">悲</rdg></app>心。即能燒一切罪根。此身滅
<lb n="0094c13" ed="T"/>後即<note n="0094043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔為〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094043"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>值佛。於彼佛土得作轉輪<note n="0094044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔聖〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聖【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094044"><lem wit="【大】">聖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>王。復
<lb n="0094c14" ed="T"/>得陀羅尼名曰<note n="0094045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（無量）＋無【宋】</note><note n="0094045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，無量無【宋】</note><app n="0094045"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">無量無</rdg></app>盡藏。復得三昧名智等。復
<lb n="0094c15" ed="T"/>得身中二十八種相。現現身不患眼舌耳鼻
<lb n="0094c16" ed="T"/>等<note n="0094046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">病＝痛【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">病【大】，痛【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094046"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">痛</rdg></app>。乃至身中一切疾病悉能消滅。若有先
<lb n="0094c17" ed="T"/>業罪者亦得消滅。若見<note n="0094047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＋（上）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天【大】，天上【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094047"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">天上</rdg></app>旱時。取烏麻子和
<lb n="0094c18" ed="T"/><note n="0094048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">毘＝稗【宋】，<g ref="#CB03915"/>【元】</note><note n="0094048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毘【大】，稗【宋】，<g ref="#CB03915"/>【元】</note><app n="0094048"><lem wit="【大】">毘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">稗</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】"><g ref="#CB03915"/></rdg></app>麻子脂。<note n="0094049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（捻）＋作【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">作【大】，捻作【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094049"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">捻作</rdg></app>丸呪一百八遍。擲著湫水中
<lb n="0094c19" ed="T"/>即得雨。若雨過多。取稻穀<note n="0094050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">炒＝燒【宋】</note><note n="0094050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">炒【大】，燒【宋】</note><app n="0094050"><lem wit="【大】">炒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">燒</rdg></app>作<note n="0094051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">華＝灰【宋】</note><note n="0094051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">華【大】，灰【宋】</note><app n="0094051"><lem wit="【大】">華</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">灰</rdg></app>。取蔓菁
<lb n="0094c20" ed="T"/>子脂和作丸。呪之一百八遍。擲著湫水中雨
<lb n="0094c21" ed="T"/>即止<note n="0094052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094052"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0094c22" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="16" type="其他">15 降伏三千大千世界魔怨印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0094053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（菩薩）＋降【宋】【元】</note><note n="0094053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">降【大】，菩薩降【宋】【元】</note><app n="0094053"><lem wit="【大】">降</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">菩薩降</rdg></app>伏三千大千世界魔怨印第十五</head>
<lb n="0094c23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0094c2301">以五指相叉。左<note n="0094054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">壓＝押【宋】</note><note n="0094054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">壓【大】，押【宋】</note><app n="0094054"><lem wit="【大】">壓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">押</rdg></app>右急把拳。當頂上著。誦
<pb n="0095a" xml:id="T20.1057b.0095a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0095a01" ed="T"/>身呪即降伏。若作此法。向舍利塔前二十九
<lb n="0095a02" ed="T"/>日夜。取白檀香作末。塗地作曼荼羅。其中散
<lb n="0095a03" ed="T"/>種種華。澡浴清淨著新淨衣。手把香鑪燒沈
<lb n="0095a04" ed="T"/>水香。面向東坐呪一千八遍。此是最初功能。
<lb n="0095a05" ed="T"/>又取芥子烏麻。著一處擣為末。以三指撮<note n="0095001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔取〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095001"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0095a06" ed="T"/>少許。呪之一遍擲著火中。如是七日日別<note n="0095002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔誦〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095002"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0095a07" ed="T"/>一百八遍。然後所作<note n="0095003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">皆悉＝悉皆【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆悉【大】，悉皆【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095003"><lem wit="【大】">皆悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">悉皆</rdg></app>成就。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0095a08" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="17" type="其他">16 廣大無畏印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0095004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（菩薩）＋廣【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">廣【大】，菩薩廣【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095004"><lem wit="【大】">廣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">菩薩廣</rdg></app>大無畏印第十六</head>
<lb n="0095a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0095a0901">起立並足。先以右手仰垂左<note n="0095005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔肘〕－【宋】</note><note n="0095005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">肘【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0095005"><lem wit="【大】">肘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>膝<note n="0095006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔頭〕－【宋】</note><note n="0095006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頭【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0095006"><lem wit="【大】">頭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。左手
<lb n="0095a10" ed="T"/>亦如之。於舍利像前。誦身呪一百八遍。即得
<lb n="0095a11" ed="T"/>無畏施於眾生。又取槐香白芥子<note n="0095007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">菖＝昌【宋】</note><note n="0095007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菖【大】，昌【宋】</note><app n="0095007"><lem wit="【大】">菖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">昌</rdg></app><note n="0095008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蒲捨＝蒱捻【宋】，莆捨【元】</note><note n="0095008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蒲捨【大】，蒱捻【宋】，莆捨【元】</note><app n="0095008"><lem wit="【大】">蒲捨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">蒱捻</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">莆捨</rdg></app>
<lb n="0095a12" ed="T"/>多婆利<note place="inline">外國藥名</note>以此等物內火中燒之。<note n="0095009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">燒火＝火燒【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">燒火【大】，火燒【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095009"><lem wit="【大】">燒火</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">火燒</rdg></app>之
<lb n="0095a13" ed="T"/>時應於佛前或在淨處。誦呪三十二遍。以香
<lb n="0095a14" ed="T"/>華供養。呪法悉皆成就。所為之者<note n="0095010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">皆悉＝悉皆【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆悉【大】，悉皆【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095010"><lem wit="【大】">皆悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">悉皆</rdg></app>剋
<lb n="0095a15" ed="T"/>果。若餘呪無驗。以此呪呪之亦皆成就。若欲
<lb n="0095a16" ed="T"/>乞夢。誦此呪并作印<note n="0095011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眠＝眼【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眠【大】，眼【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095011"><lem wit="【大】">眠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">眼</rdg></app>。即有夢隨所欲見皆
<lb n="0095a17" ed="T"/>得見之。若人無福所向不諧者。日誦三遍呪
<lb n="0095a18" ed="T"/>滿七日。諸有所求一切皆得。爾時菩薩在娑
<lb n="0095a19" ed="T"/>竭羅龍宮海會說法。見諸龍眾受大苦惱。愍
<lb n="0095a20" ed="T"/>諸龍眾為度苦惱眾生。悉得離苦無諸怨害。
<lb n="0095a21" ed="T"/>爾時龍女獻一寶珠。價直娑婆世界。為求法
<lb n="0095a22" ed="T"/>故吾為廣說離諸苦難。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0095a23" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="18" type="其他">17 水精菩薩護持千眼印咒</cb:mulu><head><note n="0095012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（千眼千臂觀世音菩薩）＋水【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">水【大】，千眼千臂觀世音菩薩水【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095012"><lem wit="【大】">水</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">千眼千臂觀世音菩薩水</rdg></app>精菩薩護持千眼印呪第十七</head>
<lb n="0095a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0095a2401">爾時水精菩薩。為欲利益護持此呪。而說呪
<lb n="0095a25" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0095a26" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT20p0095a2601">毘摩隸　摩訶毘摩隸　郁呵隸　摩訶郁呵
<lb n="0095a27" ed="T"/>隷　休摩隷　摩訶休摩隷　薩訶隷　止隷
<lb n="0095a28" ed="T"/><note n="0095013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">睇＝涕【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">睇【大】，涕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095013"><lem wit="【大】">睇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">涕</rdg></app>　馺婆訶</p>
<lb n="0095a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0095a2901">若有善男子善女人。在所遊方受持此千眼
<pb n="0095b" xml:id="T20.1057b.0095b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0095b01" ed="T"/>千臂菩薩法者。我當常隨衛護。乃至諸魔眷
<lb n="0095b02" ed="T"/>屬無惱亂者。若人急難他國相侵盜賊逆亂。
<lb n="0095b03" ed="T"/>當<note n="0095014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">取＝用【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取【大】，用【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095014"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">用</rdg></app>五色縷。結誦呪二十一遍。一遍一結繫
<lb n="0095b04" ed="T"/>於左臂。又以左手無名指中指頭指。把拳大
<lb n="0095b05" ed="T"/>母指<anchor xml:id="fxT20p0095b01"/>壓上。展小母指。指所至賊方誦呪七
<lb n="0095b06" ed="T"/>遍。悉皆退散不能為害。爾時觀世音菩薩在
<lb n="0095b07" ed="T"/>雪山中說法。觀見夜叉羅剎國中人民。唯食
<lb n="0095b08" ed="T"/>眾生血肉無有善心。菩薩為欲利益方便教
<lb n="0095b09" ed="T"/>化。眾生以神通力尋至彼國。現千眼千臂<note n="0095015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">降＋（伏）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">降【大】，降伏【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095015"><lem wit="【大】">降</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">降伏</rdg></app>
<lb n="0095b10" ed="T"/>魔身。<note n="0095016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說＝設【宋】</note><note n="0095016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">說【大】，設【宋】</note><app n="0095016"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">設</rdg></app>成就<note n="0095017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">姥＝結【宋】</note><note n="0095017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姥【大】，結【宋】</note><app n="0095017"><lem wit="【大】">姥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">結</rdg></app>陀羅尼<note n="0095018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＝印【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，印【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095018"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">印</rdg></app>。爾時羅剎國
<lb n="0095b11" ed="T"/>王。來至我所求哀頂禮。我以成就印印之。即
<lb n="0095b12" ed="T"/>得成無上道。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0095b13" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="19" type="其他">18 成就印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0095019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（觀世音菩薩）＋成【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成【大】，觀世音菩薩成【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095019"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">觀世音菩薩成</rdg></app>就印第十八</head>
<lb n="0095b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0095b1401">起立並足。合掌當心。以小指相叉左<anchor xml:id="fxT20p0095b02"/>壓右。
<lb n="0095b15" ed="T"/>誦身呪二十一遍。種種皆得成就。若救六道
<lb n="0095b16" ed="T"/>苦<note n="0095020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">難＝惱【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">難【大】，惱【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095020"><lem wit="【大】">難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">惱</rdg></app>眾生。當用輪印。以十指頭各<note n="0095021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔相〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095021"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>拄。開
<lb n="0095b17" ed="T"/>腕掌中使開。其指間各相去一寸許。即是菩
<lb n="0095b18" ed="T"/>薩在六道循環度諸苦難。以此印<note n="0095022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">輪＝轉【宋】</note><note n="0095022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輪【大】，轉【宋】</note><app n="0095022"><lem wit="【大】">輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">轉</rdg></app>迴<note n="0095023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉＋（皆）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悉【大】，悉皆【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095023"><lem wit="【大】">悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">悉皆</rdg></app>
<lb n="0095b19" ed="T"/>得離苦。此印法拔吒那羅延長年師。纔翻便
<lb n="0095b20" ed="T"/>即歸國。并將所翻之本。智通畢竟尋逐不得。
<lb n="0095b21" ed="T"/>遇於一僧邊得梵本。譯出在外無本。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0095b22" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="20" type="其他">19 成等正覺印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0095024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（千眼菩薩）＋成【宋】，（千眼千臂菩薩）＋成【元】</note><note n="0095024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成【大】，千眼菩薩成【宋】，千眼千臂菩薩成【元】</note><app n="0095024"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">千眼菩薩成</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">千眼千臂菩薩成</rdg></app>等正覺印第十九</head>
<lb n="0095b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0095b2301">結跏趺坐。先以左手舒五指。仰掌在左膝上。
<lb n="0095b24" ed="T"/><note n="0095025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔次〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095025"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>以右手舒五指。覆手捺右膝上。此與滅盡
<lb n="0095b25" ed="T"/>印法同。過去未來現在諸佛。皆同此印得佛
<lb n="0095b26" ed="T"/>菩提。此印能除一切業障。若坐禪諸法不現
<lb n="0095b27" ed="T"/>前者。當七日七夜於阿練若處。誦此陀羅尼
<lb n="0095b28" ed="T"/>并此印法。至心念佛晝夜六時懺悔即得諸
<lb n="0095b29" ed="T"/>法現前。及所得福無量無邊不可稱計。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0095c" xml:id="T20.1057b.0095c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0095c01" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="21" type="其他">20 呼召三十三天印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0095026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（千臂菩薩）＋呼【宋】，（千眼千臂菩薩）＋呼【元】</note><note n="0095026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呼【大】，千臂菩薩呼【宋】，千眼千臂菩薩呼【元】</note><app n="0095026"><lem wit="【大】">呼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">千臂菩薩呼</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">千眼千臂菩薩呼</rdg></app>召三十三天印第二十</head>
<lb n="0095c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0095c0201">先以左手四指把拳。次以右手握左手大母
<lb n="0095c03" ed="T"/>指。亦如把拳。令左手大母指。在右手虎口中
<lb n="0095c04" ed="T"/>出頭。以右手頭指來去。呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0095c05" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT20p0095c0501">唵<note place="inline">一</note>俱智俱智<note place="inline">二</note>俱耶利<note place="inline">三</note>遮利遮利<note place="inline">四</note>遮犁隷
<lb n="0095c06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">五</note>蘇婆訶</p>
<lb n="0095c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0095c0701">此陀羅尼印呪不可思議。若善男子善女人
<lb n="0095c08" ed="T"/>臨欲眠時。誦此呪一百八遍。心中所願於夢
<lb n="0095c09" ed="T"/>寐中悉得知見。若能日日誦此呪者。亦能滅
<lb n="0095c10" ed="T"/>一切罪不失菩提心。其人昏夜寐夢。漸漸增
<lb n="0095c11" ed="T"/>廣皆得吉祥。乃至夢見如來在菩提樹下<note n="0095027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">授＝受【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">授【大】，受【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095027"><lem wit="【大】">授</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">受</rdg></app>
<lb n="0095c12" ed="T"/>記成道。乃至釋梵諸天常來侍衛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0095c13" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="22" type="其他">21 呼召天龍八部鬼神印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0095028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（千眼菩薩）＋呼【宋】，（千眼千臂菩薩）＋呼【元】</note><note n="0095028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呼【大】，千眼菩薩呼【宋】，千眼千臂菩薩呼【元】</note><app n="0095028"><lem wit="【大】">呼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">千眼菩薩呼</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">千眼千臂菩薩呼</rdg></app>召天龍八部鬼神印第二十一</head>
<lb n="0095c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0095c1401">起立並<note n="0095029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（兩）＋足【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">足【大】，兩足【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095029"><lem wit="【大】">足</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">兩足</rdg></app>。先以左手大母指屈在掌中。四指
<lb n="0095c15" ed="T"/>把拳當心上著。次以右手亦如之。以右手在
<lb n="0095c16" ed="T"/>右耳邊。以頭指來去。呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0095c17" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT20p0095c1701">南無尼<note n="0095030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">健＝乾【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">健【大】，乾【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095030"><lem wit="【大】">健</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">乾</rdg></app>陀<note place="inline"><note n="0095031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔上聲〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上聲【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095031"><lem wit="【大】">上聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一</note>南無阿利闍波陀<note place="inline"><note n="0095032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔去聲〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去聲【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095032"><lem wit="【大】">去聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>二</note>馺
<lb n="0095c18" ed="T"/>婆訶<note place="inline">三</note>南無<note n="0095033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">阿＝陀【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">阿【大】，陀【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095033"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">陀</rdg></app>利闍羅馺婆訶<note place="inline">四</note><note n="0095034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">堙＝<g ref="#CB02766"/>【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">堙【大】，<g ref="#CB02766"/>【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095034"><lem wit="【大】">堙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><g ref="#CB02766"/></rdg></app>醯夷醯
<lb n="0095c19" ed="T"/><note n="0095035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔五〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095035"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">五</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>馺婆訶</p>
<lb n="0095c20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0095c2001">此呪印若善男子善女人受持讀誦者。知七
<lb n="0095c21" ed="T"/>世宿命。毒蛇不敢螫。毒藥自然除。刀不能
<lb n="0095c22" ed="T"/>害王<note n="0095036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔亦〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亦【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095036"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>不能瞋。永劫不受地獄苦。若誦此呪
<lb n="0095c23" ed="T"/>時。二十八部鬼神來詣。誦呪人邊坐聽誦呪。
<lb n="0095c24" ed="T"/>若善男子善女人。為鬼魅所著。以白縷為呪
<lb n="0095c25" ed="T"/>索。一遍一結如是四十九結。繫其咽下其病
<lb n="0095c26" ed="T"/>即除。若國內災疫流行國人死亡多者。當取
<lb n="0095c27" ed="T"/>國王園池中蓮華一百八莖。一華各<note n="0095037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呪＝誦【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呪【大】，誦【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095037"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">誦</rdg></app>一遍
<lb n="0095c28" ed="T"/>擲<note n="0095038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">著＝置【宋】【元】</note><note n="0095038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">著【大】，置【宋】【元】</note><app n="0095038"><lem wit="【大】">著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">置</rdg></app>火中。燒令蕩盡災疫即除。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0095c29" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="23" type="其他">22 解脫印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0095039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（千眼菩薩）＋解【宋】，（千眼千臂菩薩）＋解【元】</note><note n="0095039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">解【大】，千眼菩薩解【宋】，千眼千臂菩薩解【元】</note><app n="0095039"><lem wit="【大】">解</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">千眼菩薩解</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">千眼千臂菩薩解</rdg></app>脫印第二十二</head>
<pb n="0096a" xml:id="T20.1057b.0096a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0096a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0096a0101">結跏趺坐。先以左手中指。與大母指頭相捻。
<lb n="0096a02" ed="T"/>仰掌向上。餘三指散<note n="0096001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">展＝舒【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">展【大】，舒【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096001"><lem wit="【大】">展</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">舒</rdg></app>置於左膝上。次以右
<lb n="0096a03" ed="T"/>手亦如之。覆手置於右膝上。誦身呪二十一
<lb n="0096a04" ed="T"/>遍。所願悉皆滿足諸有苦惱悉皆解脫。若善
<lb n="0096a05" ed="T"/>男子善女人。具造十惡五逆等罪。如閻浮提
<lb n="0096a06" ed="T"/>履地<note n="0096002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔變為〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">變為【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096002"><lem wit="【大】">變為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>微塵。一一微塵成於一劫。是人造
<lb n="0096a07" ed="T"/>若干等罪。應墮地獄歷劫受苦永無出期。是
<lb n="0096a08" ed="T"/>善男子善女人。能於舍<note n="0096003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＋（像）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利【大】，利像【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096003"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">利像</rdg></app>及佛像前。白月
<lb n="0096a09" ed="T"/>十五日一日一夜不食。結印誦呪滿一百八
<lb n="0096a10" ed="T"/>遍。如上諸<note n="0096004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔罪〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罪【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096004"><lem wit="【大】">罪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>苦<note n="0096005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔惱〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惱【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096005"><lem wit="【大】">惱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>悉皆消滅。若不滅者無
<lb n="0096a11" ed="T"/>有是處。<note n="0096006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＋（呪）【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此【大】，此呪【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096006"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">此呪</rdg></app>印智通本上先無。智通於<note n="0096007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">涼＝原【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">涼【大】，原【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096007"><lem wit="【大】">涼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">原</rdg></app>州。
<lb n="0096a12" ed="T"/>逢一婆羅門僧有此梵本。遇會勘之更有此
<lb n="0096a13" ed="T"/>印。自得受持大有功効不可思議。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0096a14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="24" type="其他">23 自在神足印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0096008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（千眼菩薩）＋自【宋】，（千眼千臂菩薩）＋自【元】</note><note n="0096008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自【大】，千眼菩薩自【宋】，千眼千臂菩薩自【元】</note><app n="0096008"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">千眼菩薩自</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">千眼千臂菩薩自</rdg></app>在神足印第二十三</head>
<lb n="0096a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0096a1501">起立先以左手握右脚大母指如把拳。次以
<lb n="0096a16" ed="T"/>右手握左手腕背上。誦身呪七遍。欲進千里
<lb n="0096a17" ed="T"/>不以為難。誦呪之時勿令聲出。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0096a18" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="25" type="其他">24 神變自在印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0096009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（千眼菩薩）＋神【宋】，（千眼千臂菩薩）＋神【元】</note><note n="0096009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神【大】，千眼菩薩神【宋】，千眼千臂菩薩神【元】</note><app n="0096009"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">千眼菩薩神</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">千眼千臂菩薩神</rdg></app>變自在印第二十四</head>
<lb n="0096a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0096a1901">先以左手大母指捻小指甲上。次以右手亦
<lb n="0096a20" ed="T"/>如之。餘三指各散竪。合腕相著置於頂上。誦
<lb n="0096a21" ed="T"/>身呪二十一遍。皆得遊行自在。昔有罽賓國
<lb n="0096a22" ed="T"/>僧闍提。於北天竺求得此梵本。未曾翻譯。自
<lb n="0096a23" ed="T"/>得受持威力廣大不敢流傳。智通於此僧弟
<lb n="0096a24" ed="T"/>婆伽伽邊得本。依法受持功効不少。唯不
<lb n="0096a25" ed="T"/>流行於世。此本絕無。後同學得者願同功力。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0096a26" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="26" type="其他">25 王心印咒</cb:mulu><head><note n="0096010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（請千眼千臂觀世音菩薩）＋王【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王【大】，請千眼千臂觀世音菩薩王【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096010"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">請千眼千臂觀世音菩薩王</rdg></app>心印呪第二十五</head>
<lb n="0096a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0096a2701"><note n="0096011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（當以）＋兩【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兩【大】，當以兩【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096011"><lem wit="【大】">兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】">當以兩</rdg></app>手合掌虛掌內合腕。二頭指來去。呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0096a28" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT20p0096a2801">唵<note n="0096012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>阿嚕力帝囇路迦夜<note place="inline">去<note n="0096013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔聲〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聲【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096013"><lem wit="【大】">聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>毘社<note place="inline">時賀<note n="0096014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔切〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">切【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096014"><lem wit="【大】">切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>耶
<lb n="0096a29" ed="T"/><note n="0096015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096015"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>薩婆鑠覩嚧<note place="inline">二合</note>鉢囉麼馱那<note place="inline">三</note>迦囉<note n="0096016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">耶＋（四）細註【元】</note><note n="0096016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶【大】，耶<note place="inline">四</note>【元】</note><app n="0096016"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">耶<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app><g ref="#CB00292"/>
<pb n="0096b" xml:id="T20.1057b.0096b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0096b01" ed="T"/>泮莎訶</p>
<lb n="0096b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0096b0201">爾時觀世音菩薩。告諸大眾言。若佛滅後於
<lb n="0096b03" ed="T"/>末法時五百年中。閻浮提人忽眼見。及耳聞
<lb n="0096b04" ed="T"/>我此法印陀羅<note n="0096017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔尼〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0096017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0096017"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>法門者。當知此人過去
<lb n="0096b05" ed="T"/><note n="0096018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝以【宋】</note><note n="0096018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已【大】，以【宋】</note><app n="0096018"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">以</rdg></app>曾供養無量諸佛。今得值遇得我此法印
<lb n="0096b06" ed="T"/>陀羅尼。抄寫受持讀誦如法修行者。即得初
<lb n="0096b07" ed="T"/>地速成佛果。得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。爾時
<lb n="0096b08" ed="T"/>觀世音菩薩聞佛說已歡喜信受作禮而去。</p>
<lb n="0096b09" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="002" fun="close"><cb:jhead>千眼千臂觀世音菩薩陀羅尼神呪經卷下</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
